(2, 1, '2017-04-05 05:23:49', '2017-04-05 05:23:49', '<h1 style="text-align: center;">About</h1>\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-108" src="http://drzhidao.com/littlestar/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/LittleStar-Magazine-March-2017-Cover-212x300.jpg" alt="" width="879" height="1244" />\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">LittleStar Magazine, a bi-monthly, school-oriented publication that focuses on all aspects of life at international schools in Beijing, Shanghai and China at large. With in-depth stories, interesting features, up-to-date information and pictorials, LittleStar Magazine has, since its July 2005 launch, served the professional development of international schools as well as the educational needs of expatriate families who live in China. Our aim in launching LittleStar Magazine and the website is to help families make informed choices and to get more actively involved in education, which we believe will benefit the children, the schools and ultimately lead to high-quality teaching and learning.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Besides the regular magazine, LittleStar runs annual short story competition for international school students from 7 to 19 years. Each year with a different theme, students are encouraged to create short stories and compete with students from different schools. At the end of the competition, LittleStar will invite published authors or editors to be present at the awards ceremony, talking to the students about their stories and giving them practical instructions and inspiring advices.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">As Cristin Merker, one of the judges from Shanghai American School, says: "Our world is filled with stories-from television, to podcasts, books, to blogs. But our world is still missing out on a lot of stories that have yet to be written, which is why this competition is so important. It provides an outlet for our budding literary masters-YOU! Success does not always mean you win every time, it means you don’t stop and you keep editing, finessing, and writing."</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The students are the reasons we host this national English writing competition. We sincerely hope more and more students will join us, learn from each other, learn from the professionals, grow up and improve!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">LittleStar Magazine website: www.internationalschool.info</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">LittleStar Short Story Competition website: www.starshortstory.com</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">THANK YOU!!</p>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2017-04-16 02:16:32', '2017-04-16 02:16:32', '', 0, 'http://test.yahao.me/littlestar/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
